  "title": "Public Attendant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Overview:</strong></u></p><p>We are looking for a dedicated and reliable Public Area Attendant to maintain the cleanliness, hygiene, and\noverall appearance of our boutique hotel. </p><p>As part of a small and close‑knit housekeeping team, you will be responsible for keeping all public areas clean and presentable, and you may be required to assist with guest room cleaning during peak periods.</p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities include but are not limited to the following:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Clean and maintain hotel public areas including lobby, corridors, staircases, lifts, and public restrooms</li><li>Ensure cleanliness standards are consistently met throughout the day</li><li>Replenish supplies in public areas and restrooms</li><li>Identify and report maintenance or safety issues promptly</li><li>Assist the housekeeping team with guest room cleaning when required</li><li>Follow cleaning schedules, hotel standards, and safety guidelines.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Previous experience in housekeeping, cleaning, or hospitality is preferred but not required</li><li>Physically fit and able to perform manual cleaning duties</li><li>Detail‑oriented with a strong sense of cleanliness and hygiene</li><li>Reliable, punctual, and able to work independently</li><li>Team player with a flexible and positive attitude</li></ul><p><u>Why Join Us?</u></p><ul><li>Work in a friendly boutique hotel with a supportive team culture</li><li>Stable work environment with on‑the‑job training provided</li><li>Opportunity to learn hotel housekeeping operations beyond public areas</li><li>Staff benefits and hotel privileges </li></ul>",
